data.description:
Best of both worlds, Peaster ISD and close to Weatherford.  Beat this Texas heat with an upgraded three bedroom, two bath home complete with a pool that everyone can enjoy. The house is wide open for entertaining with lots of built in storage.  All of the bedrooms are spacious, with one of the secondary bedrooms having built in bunk beds.  The fenced back yard is where you will want to spend your time. The large back yard has a nice metal awning out of the back door that then moves to the sun covered seating are by the pool.  Sit down, relax, and watch the kids and their friends live their best life in the pool complete with a diving board.  All the work is done, get ready to make the move!
Buyer to verify all information.
